Privacy Policy for "Vampire Test" app

Last Updated: 06.AUG.2023

Introduction
Thank you for choosing "Vampire Test" ("we", "our", or "us"). Protecting your privacy is a priority for us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose your information when you use our app.

Information We Collect
2.1. App Activity: We gather data concerning your interactions and activity within our app to understand user behavior and improve the user experience.
2.2. Logs: We collect various types of logs that detail the app's operations to identify potential issues and enhance app functionality.
2.3. Device Information: We collect details about the type of device you're using to optimize performance and presentation.

Purpose of Data Collection
3.1. Analysis: We use the data collected to understand user preferences, behavior, and interaction with the app. This assists us in making informed decisions about improvements and feature additions.
3.2. Advertising: The collected data aids us in serving relevant and tailored ads to enhance user experience and fund the continued development and maintenance of the app.

Data Transfer
Please note that the data we collect may be transferred, stored, and processed in servers located outside of your resident jurisdiction. We take necessary steps to ensure that your data is treated securely and in agreement with this Privacy Policy.

Security
While we utilize encryption methods like SSL or TLS to protect data during transfer, no method of electronic storage or transmission is entirely secure. We strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, but we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
Our Privacy Policy may undergo updates from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: tevican.com@gmail.com
